messages.message: Is this a recent improvement on CI or did I just run into some problems, it only took 5 mins

hey Martin, looks like all the tainted files got picked up and the unit tests that got run are reasonable. I don't think there are any problems. We parallelized the unit test run with 4 processes (we added `-v -j 4` on line 456) about 2 months ago, so that could explain the speed improvement
thanks for checking. Guess I just didn't notice until more recently. Great work by the way
